text: Yelena Chernykh (née Kolesnichenko; August 24, 1979—October 4, 2011) was a Russian theatre actress. == Death == 32-year-old Yelena was killed in a car crash that took place October 4, 2011 in Novoanninsky. Together with her died her colleagues, 59-year-old Alexander Egorov and 52-year-old Valentin Yudina.Три актёра погибли в ДТП под Волгоградом At the time her death Yelena was married to Yegor Chernykh with whom she had a daughter named Anastasia Chernykh (b.2002). == References == Category:1979 births Category:2011 deaths Category:Russian stage actors Category:People from Volgograd Oblast
